<!--Hand 01 61 top left--><!--hand 02 63318 top right-->
<lb/><p>One Oclock Monday</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Oswell</p>
<lb/><p>I sent some 
<lb/>of the last sheets 
<lb/>an hour ago 
<lb/>&amp; now enclose 
<lb/>a request if you 
<lb/>can find time 
<lb/>for it and if 
<lb/>you do tell me 
<lb/>how many 
<lb/>sheets or pages 
<lb/>you want for 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002279_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>the whole of the 
<lb/>contents. Each 
<lb/>chapter is to be 
<lb/>represented by 
<lb/><hi rend="underline">two lines</hi> only</p>
<lb/><p>Will you try? 
<lb/>and oblige</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Yours ever</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">David Livingstone</p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002279_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<note type="editorial" anchored="true"><!--Hand 03-->note in different hand</note>
<lb/><p>"African stagnation from 
<lb/>same cause as that of other 
<lb/>nations - &amp; W.C.O</p>
			
